There are complicated relationships among immortals,

547
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:25,660
so some immortals can’t sit in nearby seats.

548
00:33:25,840 --> 00:33:28,500
If I arrange wrong seats for them,

549
00:33:28,940 --> 00:33:29,840
they may

550
00:33:30,260 --> 00:33:32,080
blame me

551
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:33,700
some day.

552
00:33:34,260 --> 00:33:36,400
It’s obviously a hot potato.

553
00:33:37,260 --> 00:33:39,540
Give me some suggestions.

554
00:33:42,420 --> 00:33:43,580
I have a good idea.

555
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:46,100
How about exchanging our tasks?

556
00:33:46,480 --> 00:33:47,900
You can preside at the wedding for me,

557
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:49,700
because I can’t witness their wedding

558
00:33:49,700 --> 00:33:53,120
but do nothing for Xu Feng.

559
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,052
Moon Immortal,

560
00:33:56,095 --> 00:33:58,472
Heavenly Emperor assigned it to you but not me.

561
00:33:58,540 --> 00:34:00,520
Only you can do this.

562
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:02,240
Go for it.

563
00:34:06,460 --> 00:34:08,080
Nobody can help me.

564
00:34:20,680 --> 00:34:21,660
Your Highness, you’re back.

565
00:34:22,380 --> 00:34:23,640
Is Fairy Jin Mi OK?

566
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:24,660
Yes.

567
00:34:28,240 --> 00:34:30,480
Heavenly Emperor ordered someone to send it here.

568
00:34:31,180 --> 00:34:33,240
He said this cup could turn water into tea.

569
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:36,880
His Majesty said you always liked drinking tea

570
00:34:37,820 --> 00:34:39,700
and could do something others can’t do,

571
00:34:41,720 --> 00:34:44,500
so it’s very suitable for you

572
00:34:45,060 --> 00:34:46,960
and gave it to you as the wedding gift.

573
00:34:47,900 --> 00:34:48,700
Father,

574
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:50,580
your paternal love

575
00:34:51,300 --> 00:34:52,620
is too late.

576
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:54,860
The irony is that

577
00:34:55,720 --> 00:34:58,260
when I treated him with all my heart before,

578
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:01,520
I gained nothing.

579
00:35:03,100 --> 00:35:06,460
But His Majesty still thinks highly of you.

580
00:35:10,640 --> 00:35:12,740
Because he finds

581
00:35:13,740 --> 00:35:15,140
I behave much like him,

582
00:35:16,700 --> 00:35:19,300
but I’m always his blemish left
after a night of romance.

583
00:35:20,640 --> 00:35:21,900
In his heart,

584
00:35:22,140 --> 00:35:24,960
there is always a much better son than me,

585
00:35:27,540 --> 00:35:28,540
Xu Feng.

586
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:32,520
He is magnanimous, upright, open and aboveboard.

587
00:35:32,900 --> 00:35:35,220
He doesn’t need to play tricks

588
00:35:35,380 --> 00:35:38,960
but can be praised by other immortals easily.

589
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:42,020
As a man, he’s also jealous of Xu Feng,

590
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:46,340
but, as a dad,

591
00:35:48,860 --> 00:35:51,140
he always favors Xu Feng in his heart.

592
00:35:52,240 --> 00:35:53,320
Your Highness,

593
00:35:54,940 --> 00:35:56,300
think it over.

594
00:35:56,640 --> 00:35:57,320
No need.

595
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:04,820
I won’t waste

596
00:36:05,200 --> 00:36:06,760
the efforts I made these three years.

597
00:36:10,460 --> 00:36:12,420
Notify the Bird Family and
three-direction heaven troops.

598
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:18,240
Yes.

599
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:43,920
Your Highness, the invisible sentry reports that

600
00:36:43,980 --> 00:36:45,420
the three-direction heaven troops
gather together secretly

601
00:36:45,420 --> 00:36:46,400
and the Bird Family also behaves abnormally recently.

602
00:36:46,760 --> 00:36:47,720
It seems they’ll do something great.

603
00:36:50,200 --> 00:36:53,220
Run Yu seems to be ready to rebel.

604
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:56,540
Your Highness, should we do something?

605
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,620
Let me think.

606
00:37:03,524 --> 00:37:05,818
"Sweet Spring"

607
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:52,460
Jin Mi.

608
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:11,080
Wonderful.

609
00:38:13,520 --> 00:38:14,360
Yes.

610
00:38:15,200 --> 00:38:16,469
It’s tough and smooth.

611
00:38:17,428 --> 00:38:18,554
It’s glossy but not slippery.

612
00:38:19,140 --> 00:38:20,840
If you like it,

613
00:38:21,720 --> 00:38:23,240
I can present some to you.

614
00:38:24,140 --> 00:38:25,920
I mean, this poem is wonderful.

615
00:38:27,020 --> 00:38:29,080
Don’t write love poetry.

616
00:38:29,780 --> 00:38:32,120
I write my thoughts on the plain handkerchief.

617
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:34,580
I read it again and again after writing it.

618
00:38:35,100 --> 00:38:37,700
It’s full of my worries,

619
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:41,860
but who knows it?

620
00:38:43,360 --> 00:38:44,460
It’s so easy to understand,

621
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:47,600
but who are you missing?

622
00:38:49,280 --> 00:38:51,540
So it’s not easy enough to understand.

623
00:38:53,720 --> 00:38:54,440
Yes.

624
00:38:55,580 --> 00:38:57,620
No only the handkerchief is made of fiber.

625
00:38:58,640 --> 00:39:01,280
Look at this piece of Xuan paper facing the light.

626
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:04,260
You’ll find it’s also made of fiber,

627
00:39:04,980 --> 00:39:07,960
but you refused me when I wanted
to present some to you just now.

628
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:10,740
We haven’t met for three years.

629
00:39:12,720 --> 00:39:13,620
I thought

630
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:16,560
you were still loath to meet me.

631
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:21,680
In these three years, I think a lot.

632
00:39:22,840 --> 00:39:24,100
I believe

633
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:27,820
you didn’t kill Dad.

634
00:39:28,740 --> 00:39:32,620
Water Immortal’s death is indeed related to me,

635
00:39:38,440 --> 00:39:39,180
but,

636
00:39:44,460 --> 00:39:46,480
can you refuse to marry Run Yu?

637
00:39:47,420 --> 00:39:48,400
I’ll explain his death

638
00:39:49,460 --> 00:39:51,200
to you clearly.

639
00:39:56,600 --> 00:39:58,240
Dad wanted me to marry Night Immortal,

640
00:39:59,120 --> 00:40:02,200
and Heavenly Emperor also orders me to marry him.

641
00:40:03,440 --> 00:40:04,700
I can’t refuse it.

642
00:40:07,280 --> 00:40:08,820
If I refuse,

643
00:40:09,600 --> 00:40:11,660
Heavenly Emperor will punish you again,

644
00:40:12,840 --> 00:40:14,180
and you have an ambiguous future,

645
00:40:15,200 --> 00:40:17,700
so I can’t be responsible for it.

646
00:40:18,700 --> 00:40:19,860
Anyway,

647
00:40:21,500 --> 00:40:23,320
I won’t let you marry him.
